atomTransitionMemento

类 Memento<L,E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • atomTransitionMemento.Memento<L,E>
  • 类型参数:
    L - class of central object which is supposed to be Nucleus
    E - class of physical object which is supposed to be PhysicalObject

    public class Memento<L,E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Memento stores a historical state of atom structure.
    作者:
    Shen

      • Memento

        public Memento(L centralObject,
               java.util.List<Track> tracks,
               java.util.Map<Track,java.util.List<E>> objectsInTrack,
               java.util.Map<E,java.lang.Double>[] relationBetweenCentralAndObject,
               java.util.List<Edge<E>> relationBetweenObjects)
        Constructor.
        参数:
        centralObject - central object in this historical state.
        tracks - tracks in this historical state.
        objectsInTrack - objects in tracks in this historical state.
        relationBetweenCentralAndObject - relationship between central and physical objects in this historical state.
        relationBetweenObjects - relationship between physical objects in this historical state.

        public java.util.Map<E,java.lang.Double>[] getRelationBetweenCentralAndObject()

        返回:
